1. Which statement about evaluating a Machine Learning model is the most accurate? 


-------------> ans : Model estimation involves choosing parameters that minimize the cost function.

2. The unadjusted value from estimating a linear regression model will almost always increase if more features are added.

-------------> ans : True


3. The Total Sum of Squares (TSS) can be used to select the best-fitting regression model.

-------------> ans : False


4. The Sum of Squared Errors (SSE) can be used to select the best-fitting regression model. 


-------------> ans : True


